title: SHANY 180 Color Eyeshadow Palette (180 Color Eyeshadow Palette, United Colors of SHANY, Neon Frenzy, Limited), 6.25 Ounce
description: This palette is makeup artist dreams come true. 180 highly pigmented eye shadows in every color and texture to create exciting over the top looks.
